text: Phymorhynchus oculatus is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Raphitomidae.MolluscaBase (2019). MolluscaBase. Phymorhynchus oculatus S.-Q. Zhang & S.-P. Zhang, 2017. Accessed through: World Register of Marine Species at: http://www.marinespecies.org/aphia.php?p=taxdetails&id;=1027229 on 2019-08-20 ==Description== ==Distribution== This marine species was found on a hydrothermal vent in the Manus Back-Arc Basin, Papua New Guinea ==References== ==External links== * Zhang S.-Q.
